WinRegistryKeyObj:Value.WinRegistryKeyObj:Name: Description
WinRegistryKeyObj:Value.WinRegistryKeyObj:Data: Keeps your Google software up to date. If this service is disabled or stopped, your Google software will not be kept up to date, meaning security vulnerabilities that may arise cannot be fixed and features may not work. This service uninstalls itself when there is no Google software using it.
